{"tid":2302501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動】行山跑步划艇撚，出嚟救香港啦！","createTime":"2020-11-27T07:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T12:20:22.000Z","uid":277853,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1d7ae342c40860826ffa15bf5918c751cd5f3bae","tid":2302501,"uid":277853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:11:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/106693781211036/posts/130236915523389/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F106693781211036%2Fposts%2F130236915523389%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpPtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=8d70ca01\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/106693781211036/posts/130236915523389/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXU9SD9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXU9SD9.jpg&h=2999023d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">明日大嶼前期撥款<br />\n今日過財萎會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">建制拖埋全香港人<br />\n一齊變填海大閘蟹</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你係咪好嬲？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你已經試過聯署！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你已經瘋狂喺Facebook同IG share！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你派咗好多次嬲嬲！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你係咪想知有啲咩可以做？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"pink\">換個方式繼續抗爭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"pink\">用行動話俾政府聽<br />\n我哋唔要倒錢落海</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">出嚟啦跑步撚行山撚划艇撚運動撚<br />\n<br />\n用你嘅方法發聲</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">堅持。不問結局</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#HKUTML 食魚 2020 是場虛擬運動「賽事」，旨在號召香港人為守護大嶼發聲。活動訂於11月1日至12月6日，於網上提供9條路線，讓全香港市民免費參加，以行動支持留住大嶼。<br />\n<br />\n所有參加者的累積完成距離及活動累積參與人次，會於12月底網上公佈，顯示香港人不放棄的精神！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFB: HK UTML 我哋真係好鍾意食魚 2020<br />\nIG: <a href=\"http://instagram.com/hk_utml2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhk_utml2020&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpPtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=d94364af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/hk_utml2020</a>"},{"pid":"668e2917f6f9076123011713c05da