8,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:21:54.000Z","msg":"做左無用，但好過乜都唔做<br />\n<br />\nRespect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:24:11.000Z","msg":"唔做就一定冇用<br />\n做咗就唔知嘅<br />\n<br />\n一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔係咩環保撚，但係真係好睇唔過眼條柒婆倒錢落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:07:28.000Z","msg":"正常香港係要不斷填海，起工業區、公屋、私樓<br />\n<br />\n7就7在唔識控制成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />政府誠信破產<br />\n<br />\n如果佢第一句明日大禺分四期填，第一、二期用黎起公屋、交通、鐵路，三、四期視情況起公屋/私樓，分30年填<br />\n<br />\n重點宣傳每年出幾多億、頭幾期9成土地起單位面積更大公屋、居屋<br />\n<br />\n包冇人反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcba34deedd251214f488e27a0698171f6af3501","tid":2302501,"uid":164011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5134cd76201f1026253ef6eac1692d9c603c38a6","tid":2302501,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T09:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}